## **4. ðŸ“Š Success Metrics (KPIs)**

- **Ordering Completion:** >90%
- **Payment Success:** >98%
- **Avg. Time to Order:** <3 mins
- **Notification Delivery:** >99%
- **System Uptime:** 99%+
- **Error Rate:** <3%

